snippet.title: [GOTY 2013 #10] Best VGM 1501 - Attack of the Friday Monsters! A Tokyo Tale - Opening
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Attack of the Friday Monsters! A Tokyo Tale (2013)
Opening
Hideki Sakamoto
